&lt;p&gt;同上文网址 [ Brainfuck/Ook! Obfuscation/Encoding &lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc3BsaXRicmFpbi5vcmcvc2VydmljZXMvb29r&#34;&gt;splitbrain.org]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
